# Beer image backfill: resume cursor is a local/CI re-check aid, never committed
# (a committed "all done" list would make every future run skip and never pick
# up images OFF crowd-sources later). Match report is a run artifact.
scripts/.image_backfill_state.json
beer_image_backfill.json

